alic;"&gt;“Well, I’m not sure. … I guess it’s been washed.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/16/0</guid><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 08:04:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-03-15 #4</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/15/1</link><description>&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F02a7ef40cdd60137c56b005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Yes. Will you accept a collect call from a Mr. Aaaaaaaaaa?”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/15/1</guid><pubDate>Sun, 15 Mar 2026 08:03:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-03-15 #3</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/15/0</link><description>&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F04f58b7002820138d7bb005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Bob! There’s a fly on your lip! … There he goes. …  He’s back! He’s back!”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/15/0</guid><pubDate>Sun, 15 Mar 2026 08:02:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-03-14 #2</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/14/1</link><description>&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F7d59c0f0e6f90137ce50005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;And so it went, night after night, year after year. In fact, the Hansens had been in a living hell ever since that fateful day the neighbor’s “For Sale” sign had come down and a family of howler monkeys had moved in.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/14/1</guid><pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 08:01:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-03-14 #1</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/14/0</link><description>&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F7a356390fa850137d52f005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Dave! Ain’t that your horse that kid is messin’ with?”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/14/0</guid><pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 08:00:00 -0400</pubDate></item></channel></rss>